{"tid":1615173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一城 中產shopping 好去處","createTime":"2019-10-03T04:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T02:52:56.000Z","uid":249242,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72f8e624e7855e65a24dae8a3d050db15ce9b2e4","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"有人問又一城有咩好行，作為中產人士，我就一定支持又一城購物。<br />\n<br />\n淡馬錫新加坡主權基金係業主，坡佬管理我好放心，你睇新加坡人人安居樂業，政府仲得閒到出黎說三道四就知。<br />\n<br />\n交通方便，四通八達，隔離就係九鐵站，鐵膠仲可以近距離欣賞一列列火車埋站。天橋係影相打咭的最佳位置，間唔中仲可影到直通車風馳而過。<br />\n行出去就係窩打老道，有往返九龍新界的巴士十分方便，唯一美中不足係好多車，過馬路要小心小心小心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zTYUKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zTYUKx.jpg&h=c6c07959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高級食府林立，中菜可以去八月居，要中產品味可以去Starbucks。<br />\n<br />\n豪宅區，冇TG放題，近排香港多暴徒，但九龍塘就等於半山羅便臣道，與世無爭，可以放心購物。<br />\n<br />\n位處高級學府區及名校網，隔離就係香港三大之一又一城大，感受濃厚既學術氣氛。及早為子女升學做準備，免得將來入毅進。<br />\n<br />\n講到依度係時候入Apple store 買防暴綠iPhone，你地班廢青點都阻唔到我返工搵錢shopping 架。"},{"pid":"f2938a72e44cc603e7895628ba404e8e28ce0fe1","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"屌開錯台冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b3922ffd0c3ffdd1b9ef4a5a72f5cfe5fb4c1c","tid":1615173,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"？？"},{"pid":"e611928343986372355a1488cd726d7face8a22e","tid":1615173,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"強帖留名"},{"pid":"277bc9049fc81fe5378f19d5667788a0332595d7","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b3922ffd0c3ffdd1b9ef4a5a72f5cfe5fb4c1c","tid":1615173,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"認真shopping post，一齊拯救香港零售業呀！"},{"pid":"a0d6019696acd8d1f7dfd1b300cc1c84739237a5","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"1aff9ecfa900eab3a86f5e139163eef798df6b09","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"放工又去shopping"},{"pid":"2727c1fdc4633ae90a83c3bc4abfeb87fa0c5070","tid":1615173,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"玻佬極親政權<br />\n小心小心"},{"pid":"f44e8a318ad9e02f8a131f49319bf472bbda1d4e","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"大家彌敦道shopping 轉窩打老道，去九龍塘再shopping ，咪再比d狗亂帶。"},{"pid":"8eb2bce2a45d668d7e770b2d84ce1e8ef13d2468","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"提提大家可以去下又一城shopping"},{"pid":"63a8b51448633f3263f46d1d43e42c68b529bede","tid":1615173,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxkY3dR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxkY3dR.png&h=d866a58b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支援City 呀！"}]}